metadata.name: Introvert #1/10
metadata.description:
Introvert is my Genesis NFT drop.

One of my favorite things to do is walk in nature by myself. I wrote this song recently after getting back from one such walk where my head was spinning with all the creative new opportunities web3 provides. With the spirit of experimentation top of mind, I used a method employing randomness to write a melody that I probably wouldnâ€™t have come up with on my own. I then composed the rest of the idea around that melody.

I listened back to the song while on another walk, and it really captured the feeling I get out there in nature: calm but energized and inspired. I hope this song can translate that feeling to you.
